  "keyFeatures": [
    "Free and open source under MIT license",
    "Highly configurable components tailored to your design needs",
    "127+ beautiful components inspired by Aceternity UI and Magic UI",
    "Mobile optimized and responsive across all devices",
    "Full Nuxt and Vue 3 compatibility with Composition API",
    "Built with TailwindCSS v4, motion-v, and VueUse",
    "Copy-paste approach - own and customize the code",
    "Advanced animations and special effects",
    "3D visualizations with Three.js and TresJS",
    "Community-driven with active contributions"
